summary: Remake version of fantasy cities landscape only requirement Dawnguard DLC and replace almost strange thing in skyrim.
descriptionHtml:
For anyone who first use my mod: this mod is just decorated your town that cannot be touch or move, those thing only purpose is make the town cities look more interesting and mark on map all town and cities which you can see them from far far away.
Every strange thing have it own story so you can use your imagine to make your own story about them if interested in them.
This version RECOMMENDED Dawnguard DLC (otherwise it will cause crash)
i can only give post image so all of those thing show in the image 12/13 have animation so it will be very interesting.
Thank for use my mod (sorry my english look very bad).
